From f85e641c6eb22f377bbf86e80c2318989f1d8972 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Felix Radensky <fradensky@nvidia.com>
Date: Sun, 24 May 2026 11:25:58 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] platform/mellanox: Add host-side CPLD/FPGA control
 drivers for Nvidia switches

Add nvsw core infrastructure and host-side platform drivers for
Nvidia L1, SPC5, and SPC6 switches.

The drivers expose CPLD/FPGA register access, LED control,
watchdog support, and I2C mux topology through the existing
mlxreg platform driver framework.

Signed-off-by: Felix Radensky <fradensky@nvidia.com>
Reviewed-by: Vadim Pasternak <vadimp@nvidia.com>
---
